messages.ssml: <speak>According to the Center for Disease Control and Prevention, create a household plan to help protect your health and the health of those you care about in the event of an outbreak of <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub> in your community. You should base the details of your household plan on the needs and daily routine of your household members. Visit the CDC website for a planning guide.</speak>
